Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Ashes to ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:39.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Soul to soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:50.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I will say  Never again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:58.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Remember now
