Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:21.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}sense the cry comes from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:29.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Carry your heart till the end
