Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}灰燼歸於灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:39.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}靈魂歸於靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:50.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}我將不再復述
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:58.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}請記住此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:14.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}帶著你的心到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:21.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}那讓你感受哭聲的地方
